import React from "react";
import { storiesOf } from "@storybook/react";
import Button from "./Button";


storiesOf("Button", module)
  .add("Primary", () => (
    <Button
      label="Primary"
      type="primary"
    />))
  
  .add("Secondary", () =>
    <Button
    label="Secondary"
    type="secondary"
  />)

  .add("Success", () =>
    <Button
    label="Success"
    type='success'
  />)

  .add("Danger", () =>
    <Button
    label="Danger"
    type='danger'
  />)
  
  .add("Warning", () =>
    <Button
    label="Warning"
    type='warning'
    />);
